The 2016 Vietnam Open Grand Prix, is the eleventh Grand Prix's badminton tournament of the 2016 BWF Grand Prix and Grand Prix Gold. The tournament will be held at the in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam on 18–24 July 2016 and has a total purse of $55,000.
